{"tid":432969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"官兵沉迷　解放軍封殺《王者榮耀》","createTime":"2017-10-12T03:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T08:05:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":39,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"56bba695e7f62814f036fef5b5f91c43f8df7ced","tid":432969,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20180069&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20180069%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171012&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcP%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=bdc55332\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20180069%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171012&h=8c1d4bf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20180069&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171012</a><br />\n<br />\n官兵沉迷　解放軍封殺《王者榮耀》<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171012/large/12cf04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F12cf04p.jpg&h=29c55a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少軍人沉迷騰訊旗下的手機遊戲《王者榮耀》。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n騰訊旗下手機遊戲《王者榮耀》曾被中共官媒狂轟「陷害人生」，騰訊隨後急推措施，限制青少年玩家上線時間，避免玩家過度沉迷。雖則如此，但無數玩家依然日以繼夜磨練升等，甚至連保家衞國的解放軍官兵也沉迷打機。駐疆陸軍部隊出手封殺《王者榮耀》，要令手遊絕迹軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n促將「榮耀」搬回現實<br />\n<br />\n內地官媒《人民日報》今年7月批評《王者榮耀》「釋放負能量」，是陷害人生的毒藥，要求加強網上社交遊戲監管。接着《解放軍報》亦發文批評，該手遊已滲透到官兵生活中，影響正常學習、訓練。文章指：「有些基層帶兵人反映，只要一到周末休息，有的班推門看去，幾乎全班戰士手裏捧着手機，全神貫注盯着屏幕」<br />\n內媒昨報道，在軍營最火最流行的遊戲《王者榮耀》讓大多數軍人沉迷其中、難以自拔。駐疆陸軍部隊封殺該手遊，全面禁止玩類似的網絡遊戲：「切實扼阻官兵沉溺手游的不良嗜好，將官兵的『榮耀』需求從網絡手游吸引到訓練場、圖書室、排球場、籃球場等現實舞台」。報道引述軍人網民留言，「作為一名上等兵，我覺得自己要走出《王者榮耀》，立足本職崗位，做戰場上的MVP！」<br />\n《王者榮耀》被解放軍封殺之時，卻繼續展現出驚人吸金能力，內地公司前日公佈上月App收入排行榜，《王者榮耀》續獲收入排行榜榜首。<br />\n上海澎湃新聞網"},{"pid":"0fd67648b3369b77eea1e0415c3cd82825a900c8","tid":432969,"uid":60023,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"本末倒置, 戇柒鳩"},{"pid":"74a1c0da08d7ab600ca308a5a525d21a9ad38d9f","tid":432969,"uid":51129,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334c72c2feb1649ba8d59ef2311aa26b4ec49454","tid":432969,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zynubi1k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzynubi1k&h=d192817b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0acd95260036d78965eb9e100b1c4873e03fb22f","tid":432969,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報道引述軍人網民留言，「作為一名上等兵，我覺得自己要走出《王者榮耀》，立足本職崗位，做戰場上的MVP！」</blockquote><br />\n肯肯定唔係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b807b83581d70e2573189077bdf7bddc62d44c","tid":432969,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:25:26.000Z","msg":"「上去开团！」"},{"pid":"d1d1de9edffe7d14fc4b0c67fac20556ada1c1aa","tid":432969,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"ON撚99食賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a791c23555f8623245bec583446c064612e0cc","tid":432969,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cca589f9c81d2fa971a47188970b69a3941de4b","tid":432969,"uid":49163,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"放假都唔比人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9ea4c33ad94b27236e723b3a89899d2d7cfa1b","tid":432969,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike